sentences.en: She stopped in front of a painting of a dog and she started going "woof woof"
sentences.cn: 她在一幅狗的画像前停下来，开始“汪汪”地学起狗叫来。

sentences.en: The dogs sat there without even a woof.
sentences.cn: 狗坐在那里，叫都没叫一声。

sentences.en: The horizontal threads interlaced through the warp in a woven fabric ; woof.
sentences.cn: 一种纵向的固定在织布机上的 纺线 从其中穿过的线.

sentences.en: The result was analyzed statistically by X 2 ( chi - square test ) to compare the difference between two nationalities.
sentences.cn: 用X~2检验(chi -square test)比较两个民族基因频率分布的差别,用Woof公式计算比数比 ( oddsratio, OR ) 和95%可信限(confidenceinterval,C.I. ).
